#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: _posts/2022-02-08-quarkus-2-7-1-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Quarkus 2.7.1.Final released - Maintenance release"
msgstr "Quarkus 2.7.1.Final发布 - 维护性发布"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#: _posts/2022-02-08-quarkus-2-7-1-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "2.7.1.Final is the first maintenance release for our 2.7 release train."
msgstr "2.7.1.Final是我们2.7版本列车的第一个维护版本。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2022-02-08-quarkus-2-7-1-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Today, we released Quarkus 2.7.1.Final, our first maintenance release for our 2.7 release train.\n"
"It contains bugfixes and documentation improvements, but also a couple of new features, filling a few gaps."
msgstr "今天，我们发布了 Quarkus 2.7.1.Final，这是我们 2.7 版本列车的第一个维护版本。它不仅包含错误修复和文档改进，还增加了一些新功能，填补了一些空白。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2022-02-08-quarkus-2-7-1-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "It is a safe upgrade for anyone already using 2.7."
msgstr "对于已经使用2.7的人来说，这是一次安全的升级。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2022-02-08-quarkus-2-7-1-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you are not using 2.7 already, please refer to the https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-2.7[2.7 migration guide]."
msgstr "如果你还没有使用2.7，请参考 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-2.7[2.7迁移指南] 。"

#. type: Title =
#: _posts/2022-02-08-quarkus-2-7-1-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "What's new"
msgstr "最新动态"

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2022-02-08-quarkus-2-7-1-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Kogito extensions are back"
msgstr "Kogito延长线回来了"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2022-02-08-quarkus-2-7-1-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"2.7.1.Final reintroduces the Kogito extensions that were disabled for 2.7.0.Final due to an incompatibility.\n"
"So if you are using Kogito, you can now upgrade your applications to 2.7."
msgstr "2.7.1.Final 重新引入了 2.7.0.Final 因不兼容而禁用的 Kogito 扩展。因此，如果您正在使用 Kogito，现在就可以将您的应用程序升级到 2.7。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2022-02-08-quarkus-2-7-1-final-released.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "gRPC"
msgstr "gRPC"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2022-02-08-quarkus-2-7-1-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Our gRPC extension only generated code for the application classes.\n"
"Starting with 2.7.1.Final, it also generates code from the dependencies."
msgstr "我们的 gRPC 扩展只生成应用程序类的代码。从 2.7.1.Final 开始，它还会从依赖项中生成代码。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2022-02-08-quarkus-2-7-1-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "OIDC token propagation"
msgstr "OIDC 令牌传播"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2022-02-08-quarkus-2-7-1-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We introduced a reactive counterpart to the OIDC token propagation extension,\n"
"that you can use with RESTEasy Reactive."
msgstr "我们引入了与 OIDC 令牌传播扩展相对应的反应式扩展，您可以将其与 RESTEasy Reactive 结合使用。"

